These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, card-games, fishing
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, oliveros, baccarat, dannemann
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, house, r&b, trance
4 different pets are kept: cat, fish, frog, rabbit
1. the oliveros-smoker is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the fan of trance is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the fan of r&b is the vegafina-smoker##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
5. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
6. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of house##1
7. the oliveros-smoker is the owner of the cat##1
8. the fan of house is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
9. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | board-games  | fishing  | camping | card-games |
| Cigar           | oliveros | vegafina | dannemann  | baccarat  |
| Music-Genre   | trance       | r&b      | country | house      |
| Pet           | cat          | fish     | frog    | rabbit     |

