.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, engineer, firefighter, scientist
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, action, romance, satire
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, dutch, thai, turkish
4 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, guinea-pig, horse
1. the thai is on the left of the bartender##1
2. the firefighter is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far right##1
4. the scientist is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
6. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the engineer##1
7. the scientist is on the right of the bartender##1
8. the australian is on the far right##1
9. the owner of the guinea-pig is the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Job           | engineer   | bartender  | scientist | firefighter |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | satire       | action       | time-travel     |
| Nationality   | thai       | turkish    | dutch     | australian  |
| Pet           | ferret     | guinea-pig | horse     | cat         |

