 7. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1
 8. the person traveling to hamburg is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 9. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
10. the person driving the train is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
